\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6}{\ignorespaces RMSE variability across seeds. With only a single seed (42), there is no stochastic spread. Future sweeps should use 3--5 seeds for top candidates to quantify variability and ensure rankings are robust.}}{11}{figure.caption.12}\protected@file@percent }
